                              [.presnt sinple.]
    
  s / es
  har doim uchinchi shaxs birlikda ishlatiladi 
  felning o`zagi s/es qo`shladi 
  
         he 
         she      dous 
         it 
  
         we 
         you      do
         the
 
                                [.Past simple.] 
                             
past senplning     sobjekt + verb(ed/ps) + objekt
 
Q1= {o`tkan odiy zamon} 
o`tkan zamonda sodir bo`lgan ishharakatlardi ifodalasha uchun ishaltiladi          

M= Tom lost the key of his house 
M= My friend didnt see me in school the other day.
M= did Jane win the contest three days ego?

Q2= {o`tkan oddiy zamon }
o`tkan zamonda sodir bo`lagan voqealardi hikoya
qilish uchun ishlatiladi 

M= After the lesson I went home, hed dineer but did not go to bed. 































                 
